nne of Tyrosh</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Calla_Blackfyre&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Prior to the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"First Blackfyre Rebellion\">First Blackfyre Rebellion</a>, Calla's father <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon</a> agreed to <a href=\"/index.php/Marriage\" title=\"Marriage\">wed</a> her to her half-uncle, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Aegor_Rivers\" title=\"Aegor Rivers\">Aegor Rivers</a>. However, it is unknown if and when the marriage took place.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_daeron_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/62/Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg/300px-Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"360\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/62/Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg/450px-Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg 1.5x, /images/6/62/Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Calla_Blackfyre_by_archamion.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Calla Blackfyre by archamion ©</div></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Calla_Bla